release.changelog: Hello to the Little Star Edition update! With this update, we've made various improvements throughout the app. There were some bugs, and we've chased them away! Additionally, we've added a new page called the 'Security Dashboard.' On this page, we recommend award-winning S and A tier antivirus applications for your security, without any sponsorship. We also provide shortcuts for quick access if you use any of them.
